WEBVTT

00:02.464 --> 00:03.637
Excuse me.

00:04.161 --> 00:07.456
Can you tell me how to get to the shopping area from here?

00:07.927 --> 00:08.616
Sure.

00:09.210 --> 00:10.740
Go straight down the street.

00:12.016 --> 00:12.577
OK.

00:12.804 --> 00:14.483
Straight down this street.

00:15.123 --> 00:17.069
Turn left at the second traffic light.

00:17.830 --> 00:18.317
Okay.

00:18.525 --> 00:22.629
Straight down this street and turn left at the second traffic light.

00:23.013 --> 00:25.245
You will see the police station on your left.

00:25.809 --> 00:27.098
Okay, got it.

00:27.437 --> 00:31.315
Right next to the police station, you will see a large blue building.

00:31.740 --> 00:32.094
Okay.

00:32.304 --> 00:33.875
A large blue building.

00:34.329 --> 00:36.115
That's Blue Note Shopping Center.

00:36.892 --> 00:37.891
Thank you so much.

00:38.157 --> 00:39.696
I really appreciate it.

